          print library linking information\"\n        echo \"  --cflags         print pre-processor and compiler flags\"\n        echo \"  --prefix         print the installation prefix\"\n        echo \"  --exec-prefix    print the executable installation prefix\"\n        echo \"  --libdir         print the library installation directory\"\n        echo \"  --includedir     print the include directory\"\n        echo \"  --help           print this help message\"\n        ;;\n    *)\n        # If no arguments or unknown argument, show help\n        echo \"Usage: gpgme-config [OPTION]\" >&2\n        echo \"Try 'gpgme-config --help' for more information.\" >&2\n        exit 1\n        ;;\nesac\nEOF\n    chmod +x /usr/local/bin/gpgme-config"})
